cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper is about face recognition using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a novel loss function for feature discrimination, which is a core problem in deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves designing a new loss function, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on face recognition benchmarks, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves adapting the loss function to emphasize mis-classified points, which is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
